acceptanceCriteria:
At stream start, emit `event: message_start
data: {"type":"message_start","message":{"id":"...","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[],"model":"<model>","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0}}}

` followed by `event: content_block_start
data: {"type":"content_block_start","index":0,"content_block":{"type":"text","text":""}}

`

For each `data: {...}` line with `choices[0].delta.content` text, emit `event: content_block_delta
data: {"type":"content_block_delta","index":0,"delta":{"type":"text_delta","text":"<chunk>"}}

`

The OpenAI `[DONE]` sentinel is consumed but not forwarded; instead, at end-of-stream emit `event: content_block_stop
data: {"type":"content_block_stop","index":0}

` and `event: message_stop
data: {"type":"message_stop"}

`
